foia:ProcessedRequestSection.foia:FootnoteText: Column one should be the same number as the number of pending FOIA requests reported by each component at the end of FY08. The differences in numbers for AF, ARMY, CENTCOM, DIA, DISA, DSS, JFCOM, NAVY, NORTHCOM, OSD/JS, PACOM, SOCOM, and STRATCOM are due to better accounting methods and re-classifying some cases as consultations which caused some minor discrepancy in starting numbers.
